    <item>
      <title>日本抗议韩国法院对殖民时代工人的裁决</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-28/japan-protests-south-korean-court-ruling-on-colonial-era-workers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本外务省召见韩国驻东京大使馆的一名高级外交官，抗议最高法院的一项裁决，即日本公司应向在殖民占领期间被征召入伍的韩国人支付赔偿金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-28/japan-protests-south-korean-court-ruling-on-colonial-era-workers</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 05:33:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>西方国家撤离俄罗斯后，小企业主获得 10 亿美元奖金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-28/small-business-owner-lands-1-billion-prize-after-russia-business-exodus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[企业家阿列克谢·萨加尔（Alexey Sagal）度过了他职业生涯中最成功的一年半，他的阿内斯特集团（Arnest Group）成为弗拉基米尔·普京总统入侵乌克兰后国际企业撤离俄罗斯的最大受益者之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-28/small-business-owner-lands-1-billion-prize-after-russia-business-exodus</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>科罗拉多州共和党人博伯特将于 2024 年切换选区参选</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-28/colorado-republican-boebert-switching-districts-to-run-in-2024</link>
      <description><![CDATA[来自科罗拉多州的直言不讳的保守派共和党众议员劳伦·博伯特表示，她明年将竞选连任——但在不同的地区。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-28/colorado-republican-boebert-switching-districts-to-run-in-2024</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 03:20:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
