    <item>
      <title>米莱以广泛的改革法案轰动阿根廷国会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-28/milei-blitzes-argentina-s-congress-with-far-ranging-reform-bill</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿根廷总统哈维尔·米莱周三向国会提交了一项内容广泛的综合改革方案，将其休克疗法从经济政策扩展到政府的各个方面。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-28/milei-blitzes-argentina-s-congress-with-far-ranging-reform-bill</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 00:08:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国在今年最后一揽子计划中向乌克兰提供价值 2.5 亿美元的武器</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-27/us-provides-250-million-in-ukraine-arms-in-year-s-last-package</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拜登政府周三宣布向乌克兰提供价值 2.5 亿美元的武器和装备，这是今年的最后一揽子计划，官员们敦促国会在新的一年里继续提供援助。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-27/us-provides-250-million-in-ukraine-arms-in-year-s-last-package</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 21:01:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国最高政治咨询机构罢免三名国防高管</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-27/top-china-political-advisory-exiles-three-aerospace-executives</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国最高政治咨询机构将导弹制造公司的三名高级领导人从全国委员会中除名，这是中国军队高层内部动荡的最新迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-27/top-china-political-advisory-exiles-three-aerospace-executives</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 13:10:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>刚果警察与抗议者发生冲突，选举游行变得丑陋</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-27/drc-police-opposition-clash-as-election-protest-turns-ugly</link>
      <description><![CDATA[刚果民主共和国首都的一场小规模选举抗议活动演变成暴力事件，示威者向安全部队投掷石块，安全部队则发射催泪瓦斯，并袭击了反对派总统候选人马丁·法尤鲁的总部。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-27/drc-police-opposition-clash-as-election-protest-turns-ugly</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 11:31:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列对加沙中部和南部发动猛烈袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2023-12-27/urgent-israel-launches-heavy-strikes-across-central-and-southern-gaza-after-widening-its-offensive</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加沙地带代尔巴拉赫（美联社）巴勒斯坦卫生官员表示，以色列军队对加沙地带中部和南部地区发动猛烈袭击，造成数十人死亡，周三，数千名巴勒斯坦家庭逃离以色列对加沙仅存的几处拥挤的避难所不断扩大的地面攻势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2023-12-27/urgent-israel-launches-heavy-strikes-across-central-and-southern-gaza-after-widening-its-offensive</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 11:23:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
